thread.title: Jens Lange
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Jens Lange

author: Jens Lange
title: Jens Lange
text:
Consistently excellent service from your staff, best prices on quality gear and reliable, timely dispatch of purchased items. Thanks Store DJ.
Furthermore really appreciate that you use Australia Post as this ensures reliable and speedy delivery of purchased goods - rarely the case with couriers in my experience.
